modules.description: This module supports arithmetic and mathematical operations on dual numbers, represented as records with `re` (real) and `dre` (dual) components, both as double-precision floats. It provides basic arithmetic, exponentiation, logarithms, trigonometric and hyperbolic functions, along with Newton-Raphson root-finding, enabling applications in automatic differentiation and numerical analysis where precise derivative calculations or iterative solutions to nonlinear equations are required.
